<P>LOVE in the EAST; OR, Adventures of Twelve Hours: A COMIC OPERA, IN THREE ACTS.</P>
<P>WRITTEN BY THE AUTHOR OF THE STRANGERS AT HOME.</P>
<P>AS PERFORMED AT THE Theatre-Royal, Drury-Lane.</P>
<P>LONDON: PRINTED FOR W. LOWNDES, NO. 77, FLEET-STREET. MDCCLXXXVIII. PRICE 1s. 6d.</P>
</DIV1>
